32
00:01:59,127 --> 00:02:01,210
<i>I realized, Michael...</i>

33
00:02:01,377 --> 00:02:05,419
<i>...that I had emerged, not through
the doors of Kenner, Bach & Ledeen...</i>

34
00:02:05,585 --> 00:02:08,877
