465
00:32:09,460 --> 00:32:11,710
Todd, could I get that coffee now?

466
00:32:13,919 --> 00:32:18,044
Who is this guy they sent from New York?
Clayton? I never heard of him.

467
00:32:19,835 --> 00:32:21,294
Michael Raymond Clayton.

468
00:32:21,460 --> 00:32:26,335
<i>Born September 9, 1959,
St. Joseph's Hospital, Bronx, New York.</i>

469
00:32:26,502 --> 00:32:30,210
<i>Father is NYPD patrolman Raymond Xavier Clayton.</i>

470
00:32:30,377 --> 00:32:33,044
