476
00:32:51,127 --> 00:32:53,085
<i>...Organized Crime Task Force.</i>

477
00:32:53,252 --> 00:32:56,627
And then in 1990, he starts at Kenner, Bach & Ledeen.

478
00:32:56,794 --> 00:32:58,252
So he's a partner?

479
00:32:59,127 --> 00:33:01,627
